**** Metric Adjustment Files for Japanese TeX

All files whose name start with 't' is for vertical writing directinarily.

* For Zeit format fonts:
   asiya24.adj         Asiya font
   mincho.adj          Watanabe vectory font
   
* For JG format fonts:
   jg.adj              For all JG fons

* For TrueType format fonts:
   dfhs*.adj           DylaLab, DynaFont, Heisei Series
   df{mim,got}p*.adj   DynaLab, DynaFont, Kakou Series
   f5ajch*.adj         Fujitsu, FontCity, Heisei Series
   hgrh*.adj           Ricoh, TrueType World, Heisei Series

* X Window System PCF/BDF format fonts:
   k14.adj             k14.{pcf,bdf}
   jiskan*.adj         jiskan{16,24}.{pcf,bdf}

* Dummy (or, template file):
   empty.adj
   none.adj
